    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Subject: SIGHTING OF OBJECT RESEMBLING",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "FLYING SAUCER ON APRIL 6, 1956,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "NEAR HENDERSON, NORTH CAROLINA",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "(ESPIONAGE)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "On April 6, 1956, Miss [REDACTED] an",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "employee of this Bureau who resides at [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Alexandria, Virginia, while en route to Morven, North Carolina,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "via automobile, with her fiance, Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "observed an unusual object which appeared to resemble a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "flying saucer.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Miss [REDACTED] stated at about 5 A.M., on April 6,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "1956, while it was still dark and while driving on Route 1",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "north of Henderson, North Carolina, she and Mr. [REDACTED] were",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "startled by what appeared to be an oval-shaped, low-flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "object coming directly toward their car at a great speed,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "on the driver's side. Miss [REDACTED] stated the object,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "which was less than 25 feet from the ground, appeared to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "be spinning, was bright as though containing a series of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "lights in a zigzagging pattern, was light blue in color",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "and was at least as wide as the highway and no more than",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "from two to four feet in thickness. She stated the object",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "did not change shape, it made no sound and that she observed",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "it for only a few seconds before it appeared to pass over the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "car, accelerate speed and veer off out of sight behind them.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Miss Richards advised when daylight came she noticed it was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "cloudy and that approximately 30 minutes after they had",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "sighted the object it began to rain.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "status": "blank"
    },
